## Venv Warning
The venv was recreated on 2026-03-29 because the project was renamed from
`squeaky_wheel` to `grit`, which broke the old venv's activate script (hardcoded
old path). If the venv ever stops working, check `venv/pyvenv.cfg` and
`grep VIRTUAL_ENV venv/bin/activate` ‚Äî the path must match the actual directory.
There is also a stale Streamlit 1.32.0 installed in the user site-packages at
`~/Library/Python/3.13/lib/python/site-packages/` which will take over if the
venv isn't activated properly. The system install should ideally be removed with
`python3 -m pip uninstall streamlit` (without the venv active).

## Key Files
- `app.py` ‚Äî Streamlit frontend (3343 lines, 13 tabs)
- `build_schema.py` ‚Äî initialises SQLite tables (idempotent, called on every app start)
- `sync_data.py` ‚Äî nightly data sync (TheyVoteForYou API ‚Üí SQLite)
- `grit_cache.db` ‚Äî local database (committed to repo for portability)
- `requirements.txt` ‚Äî pip dependencies (streamlit>=1.40.0, no streamlit-searchbox)
- `assets/` ‚Äî logo PNGs (`logo_dark_bg.png`, `logo_light_bg.png`, `parrot_icon.png`)

## App Architecture
`app.py` runs top-to-bottom on every interaction. Structure:
1. Imports and `st.set_page_config`
2. CSS injection for input borders
3. `build_schema.init_db()` ‚Äî ensures all tables exist
4. Helper functions (`query`, `postcode_to_state`, `_haversine`, `electorate_card`, etc.)
5. Header: logo via `st.image("assets/logo_dark_bg.png")`, value proposition box, mandate countdown
6. Compare banner (conditional)
7. `st.tabs()` ‚Äî creates 13 tabs
8. Tab content blocks (`with tab_*:`) ‚Äî each renders its own UI

